<h2>Full-Service Real Estate Legal Support</h2>
<p>Our law firm provides comprehensive real estate legal services specifically tailored to areas beyond real estate settlement services. Our expertise is deeply rooted in Pennsylvania law, ensuring our clients receive top-tier legal support.</p>
<h2>Our Real Estate Services</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Lease Drafting and Review</strong> — We focus on drafting and reviewing lease agreements, ensuring they align with Pennsylvania law and safeguard our clients' interests. This encompasses lease negotiation, tenant and landlord rights, and managing lease renewals and terminations.</li>
    <li><strong>Landlord-Tenant Matters</strong> — Our firm handles a wide range of landlord-tenant issues, including dispute resolution, eviction proceedings, and enforcement of lease terms.</li>
    <li><strong>Assessment Appeals</strong> — We help with commercial and residential assessment appeals in Westmoreland and Allegheny Counties.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="/practice-areas/for-sale-by-owner/">For Sale By Owner Transactions</a></strong> — Our attorneys can craft the Agreement of Sale to fit your needs when buying or selling without a realtor. <a href="/downloads/pa-fsbo-sellers-checklist.pdf">Download our free FSBO checklist</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Real Estate Investment and Development</strong> — We provide legal counsel for real estate investments and development projects, focusing on due diligence and adherence to state real estate laws.</li>
</ul>
